casebody.data:
Gregory Massie, Respondent, v General Motors Corporation, Appellant, et al., Defendant.

— Appeal from an order of the Supreme Court, Dutchess County (Jiudice, J.), dated August 4, 1980, dismissed, without costs or disbursements, as academic (see Massie v General Motors Corp., 88 AD2d 1110). Weinstein, J. P., Gulotta, O’Connor and Rubin, JJ., concur.
